Plugin system for python.

For more details see the example directory (it's a plugin)

All plugin has a separated directory (ex.: example)
The pluginloader module load plugins from the specified directory.
It's load only the selected directory names (or all).


Usage:

from plygin import pluginloader 
pluginloader.pluginModule = "exampleproj.plugins" # Where are your plugins? 
pluginloader.activePlugins = [...] # directory names of your plugins. ex: "example1", "example2" 
pluginloader.loadPlugins() #load the plugins

